understanding this properly.

00:03:22.551 --> 00:03:25.476
So this is n,

00:03:26.202 --> 00:03:28.122
and then this is going to be g of n,

00:03:28.122 --> 00:03:29.213
right over here.

00:03:29.532 --> 00:03:31.610
So, when n is equal to one,

00:03:32.234 --> 00:03:34.407
when n is equal to one,
g of n is going to be,

00:03:34.407 --> 00:03:37.012
or g of one is going to be
the number of party favors

00:03:37.012 --> 00:03:40.005
Seo-Yun had before the first guest.

00:03:40.730 --> 00:03:43.824
Well, before the first guest,
she had 50 party favors.

00:03:44.428 --> 00:03:45.775
She had 50 party favors.

