Now, the second guest comes.

00:03:48.755 --> 00:03:50.584
Now the number of party
favors she had before

00:03:50.584 --> 00:03:54.444
the second guest, well,
she had to give three

00:03:54.444 --> 00:03:56.313
to the first guest, so she's now

00:03:56.313 --> 00:03:58.676
going to have 47 party favors.

00:03:59.320 --> 00:04:00.824
Now, when n is equal to three,

00:04:00.824 --> 00:04:02.429
how many party favors did she have

00:04:02.429 --> 00:04:04.568
before the third guest?

00:04:04.928 --> 00:04:06.390
Well, she would've had
to give party favors

00:04:06.390 --> 00:04:08.835
