guest, who each got three.

00:04:09.194 --> 00:04:13.486
So, she would have 44, and
I think you see the pattern.

00:04:13.928 --> 00:04:17.022
For every time n, when n
equals one, g of n is 50,

00:04:17.199 --> 00:04:19.596
and every time we increase n by one,

00:04:19.596 --> 00:04:23.497
