00:04:23.497 --> 00:04:28.237
g of n by plus three, by
minus three, I should say

00:04:28.475 --> 00:04:30.838
because she's giving away
party favors, minus three.

00:04:31.665 --> 00:04:32.646
Minus three.

00:04:33.006 --> 00:04:35.058
So because the difference
between successive terms

00:04:35.058 --> 00:04:37.460
